text: A Friend's Father who is 70+ in age had his 2 Covaxin Shots and didn't fall sick. Now, as he is a Medical Practitioner, the 3rd Booster shot was given and they gave Covishield. He had Fever, Body pains for 2 days and then recovered. Something to think about. #CovidVaccine
